<i>♪ Stayin' alone and doing
the best I can</i> ♪

49:17.830 --> 49:22.210
<i>♪ I shipped my trunk
down to Tennessee</i> ♪

49:23.711 --> 49:27.715
<i>♪ I shipped my trunk down
